				\begin{document}$${\mathrm{IRR}}_{\mathrm{area}}=\frac{{\mathrm{IRR}}_{\mathrm{prod}}}{{\mathrm{IRR}}_{\mathrm{effi}}}+\mathrm{LR}$$\end{document}with IRRarea, IRRprod, and LR given in (km3 year−1) and IRReffi in percentage (%).

